					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Let it snow, Let it snow, Let it snow&#8230;</p> <p>With thanks to all those in the chat who read this:</p> <p>-Chicken<br /> -Hippo<br /> -red-rogue<br /> -MaliceAfterthought<br /> -SpookyPizza<br /> -AidenEldritch<br /> -Freaky<br /> -Timberbuff</p> <p>Thanks also to Cimmerian, who suggested getting rid of all my blackboxes.</p> <p>This is easily the most ambitious SCP I've attempted thus far, so I'm sure it's going to garner a hefty number of downvotes. I completely understand such a decision :p.</p> <p>Regarding the images:</p> <p>-The image in Document 1 is found <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Blizzard1_-_NOAA.jpg">here</a>, and is in the public domain.<br /> -The image in Document 2 is found <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Snowflake9.png">here</a>, and is in the public domain.<br /> -The image in Document 3 is found <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Blizzard2_-_NOAA.jpg">here</a>, and is in the public domain.<br /> -The image in Document 4 is found <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:USS_Philippine_Sea_(CV-47)_flight_deck_with_snow_Nov_1950.jpg">here</a>, and is in the public domain.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
